3) Performance/quality improvement on a core workflow (ownership: diagnose → prioritize → implement → measure): I analyzed where work was stalling and where errors were occurring, identified the highest-leverage fixes, and implemented changes with clear success metrics. Outcome: improved throughput and reduced error/rework, with a clear before/after dashboard to track progress.
